<title>USA: Heartsoft to buy back 500,000 shr block.</title>
<headline>Heartsoft to buy back 500,000 shr block.</headline>
<dateline>TULSA, Okla. 1997-02-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Heartsoft Inc said Wednesday it plans to repurchase a block of 500,000 shares of its common stock.</p>
<p>The company said it is in negotiations with one of its larger shareholders to repurchase the 500,000 share block at or near par value.</p>
<p>&quot;The number of shares of Heartsoft common stock issued and outstanding has grown over the last 18 months as the company entered into certain agreements with key executives,&quot; Chairman and Chief Executive Benjamin Shell said in a statement.</p>
<p>The repurchase of 500,000 shares represents about 10 percent of the company's outstanding shares.</p>
